snippet.title: Diana and Maggie learn how to compromise and share when they both want the same dress
snippet.description:
Diana & Maggie want the same dress. Roma sews the same dress for Maggie with a sewing machine toy. At the end they both have beautiful princess dresses and accessories to wear!
